{"_id":"tech-sound-02-ballade-des-arcs-brises","name":"Ballade des arcs brisés","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-notes-sound-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Son","breathKey":"sound","breathLabel":"Souffle du Son","form":2,"costE":8.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"3d6 + Finesse","damageText":"3d6 + Finesse\n\nFendre\n*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée","range":3.0,"rangeText":"3m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Son","description":"L'épéiste les tranche dans une rotation circulaire, coupant tout ce qui se trouve dans un rayon de 10 pieds autour d'eux.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sound","aoe"],"specialLines":["Fendre","*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"allInRange","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":true,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sound-03-prelude-d-un-cauchemar","name":"Prélude d'un cauchemar","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-notes-sound-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Son","breathKey":"sound","breathLabel":"Souffle du Son","form":3,"costE":4.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"2d8 + Force","damageText":"2d8 + Force","range":4.5,"rangeText":"4.5m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Son","description":"Le tueur frappe rapidement et rétracte son épée avec sa chaîne dans un mouvement de fouet qui tranche immédiatement la cible.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sound"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sound-04-des-coups-retentissants-et-constants","name":"Des coups retentissants et constants","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-notes-sound-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Son","breathKey":"sound","breathLabel":"Souffle du Son","form":4,"costE":7.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"2d8 + Force","damageText":"2d8 + Force","range":7.5,"rangeText":"7.5m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Son","description":"Les lames des tueurs se déplacent dans un flou de mouvement, créant une symphonie de sons tranchants tandis qu'ils déchaînent un déluge de coups rapides et incessants. Chaque coup résonne avec une intensité assourdissante, créant des ondes de choc qui fracassent l'air environnant et désorientent leurs adversaires.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sound"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sound-05-performance-des-cordes","name":"Performance des cordes","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-notes-sound-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Son","breathKey":"sound","breathLabel":"Souffle du Son","form":5,"costE":10.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"3d6 + Finesse","damageText":"3d6 + Finesse","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Son","description":"Les lames du Tueur deviennent une extension de son corps grâce à leur fluidité. Les chaînes métalliques qui les relient vibrent au rythme d'une musique, produisant des sons résonnants qui subliment les mouvements et les frappes du Tueur. Ses attaques sont une symphonie de coups harmonieux.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sound"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sound-06-requiem","name":"Requiem","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/trades/music-notes-sound-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Son","breathKey":"sound","breathLabel":"Souffle du Son","form":6,"costE":17.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"3d8 + Finesse","damageText":"3d8 + Finesse\n\nFendre\n*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Son","description":"Les lames du Tueur se déplacent avec solennité et mesure, tranchant tout dans un rayon de 4,5 mètres autour de lui. Chaque coup est lourd de sens, produisant des échos lugubres qui résonnent sur le champ de bataille. Les mouvements du Tueur sont gracieux et puissants, car il canalise son chagrin et sa détermination dans ses attaques.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sound","aoe"],"specialLines":["Fendre","*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"allInRange","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":true,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"techInsect0001","name":"Danse du Papillon : Caprice","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Insecte","breathKey":"insect","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Insecte","form":1,"costE":5.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8 + Finesse","damageText":"1d8 + Finesse\n\nAffliction\n* Provoque un statut modifié","range":4.5,"rangeText":"4.5m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Insecte","description":"L'épéiste saute en avant vers l'adversaire, le piquant plusieurs fois avec la lame pour injecter du poison.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","insect","affliction","poison"],"specialLines":["Affliction","* Provoque un statut modifié"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":1,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
