{"_id":"tech-insect-03-danse-de-la-libellule-hexagone-de-l-il-compos","name":"Danse de la Libellule : Hexagone de l'Œil Composé","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Insecte","breathKey":"insect","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Insecte","form":3,"costE":9.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"3d6 + Force","damageText":"3d6 + Force\n\n3x Affliction\n* Provoque un statut modifié","range":3.0,"rangeText":"3m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Insecte","description":"Une attaque basée sur six frappes où l'utilisateur attaque la cible à six endroits différents du corps afin d'injecter du poison mortel à chaque zone, augmentant ainsi les chances que la cible succombe au poison.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","insect","affliction","poison"],"specialLines":["3x Affliction","* Provoque un statut modifié"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":3,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-insect-04-danse-du-mille-pattes-zigzag-aux-cent-pattes","name":"Danse du Mille-pattes : Zigzag aux Cent Pattes","type":"technique","img":"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Insecte","breathKey":"insect","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Insecte","form":4,"costE":18.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"4d8 + Finesse","damageText":"4d8 + Finesse\n\nPoursuivant\n*Impossible de réagir ou d'esquiver\n\nAffliction\n* Provoque un statut modifié","range":9999,"rangeText":"Pas de limite","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Insecte","description":"L'épéiste court à pleine vitesse en un motif en zigzag pour générer assez d'élan, créant une puissante poussée unique qui injecte simultanément du poison dans la victime ciblée. La vitesse aveuglante et le motif erratique servent également à semer la confusion chez l'adversaire et à créer une ouverture adéquate.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","insect","affliction","poison"],"specialLines":["Poursuivant","*Impossible de réagir ou d'esquiver","Affliction","* Provoque un statut modifié"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":true,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":true,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":1,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
