{"_id":"tech-moon-08-dragon-a-queue-annelee","name":"Dragon à Queue Annelée","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-moon.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Lune","breathKey":"moon","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Lune","form":8,"costE":13.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d20 + Force/Finesse","damageText":"1d20 + Force/Finesse\n\nÀ distance\n*Peut être utilisé à partir de la portée de mêlée jusqu'à la distance autorisée","range":7.5,"rangeText":"7.5m","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Lune","description":"L'épéiste se balance dans un arc élevé, envoyant une puissante frappe à longue portée qui laisse derrière elle de nombreuses lames de lune sur son passage.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","moon","ranged"],"specialLines":["À distance","*Peut être utilisé à partir de la portée de mêlée jusqu'à la distance autorisée"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":true,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-moon-09-chemin-de-la-lune-decroissante","name":"Chemin de la Lune Décroissante","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-moon.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Lune","breathKey":"moon","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Lune","form":9,"costE":1.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d12 + Force","damageText":"1d12 + Force","range":1.5,"rangeText":"1.5m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Lune","description":"L'épéiste frappe à plusieurs reprises à proximité, enchaînant coups après coups dans une séquence implacable. Chaque attaque est conçue pour légèrement chevaucher la précédente.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","moon"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
