{"_id":"tech-sun-08-estoc-de-la-fleur-solaire","name":"Estoc de la Fleur Solaire","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-flame-ring-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":8,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"L'utilisateur effectue un coup de lame précis en utilisant la pointe de sa lame pour atteindre la cible.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sun-09-dragon-du-halo-solaire-tete-dansante","name":"Dragon du Halo Solaire - Tête Dansante","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-flame-ring-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":9,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"Le joueur adopte une position de garde élevée, puis déploie une série de coups de lame successifs en un mouvement fluide, évoquant un dragon japonais né des flammes du soleil. Cette technique permet de décapiter plusieurs cibles simultanément.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sun-10-roue-de-feu","name":"Roue de Feu","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-flame-ring-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":10,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"Le joueur effectue un saut périlleux en arrière derrière l'adversaire avant de décocher une attaque verticale circulaire rapide qui coupe l'adversaire en deux.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sun-11-arc-en-ciel-factice","name":"Arc-En-Ciel Factice","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-flame-ring-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":11,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"Le joueur effectue des rotations et des mouvements de torsion à grande vitesse, créant ainsi des images fantomatiques qui servent principalement à esquiver les attaques. Ces images fantomatiques sont particulièrement efficaces contre les ennemis à la vision très perçante.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-sun-12-valse-enflammee","name":"Valse enflammée","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-flame-ring-yellow.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":12,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"Une combinaison de deux coups qui commence par une attaque verticale descendante suivie immédiatement d'une attaque horizontale.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"techSun13Form1","name":"Treizième Forme","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-whip.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle du Soleil","breathKey":"sun","breathLabel":"Souffle du Soleil","form":13,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Force / Finesse","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle du Soleil","description":"Le joueur exécute successivement et de manière répétée les douze formes de la respiration solaire afin d'améliorer la précision et l'agilité de ses mouvements et de ses attaques.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","sun"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-01-pas-leger","name":"Pas Léger","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":1,"costE":4.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d6 + Finesse","damageText":"1d6 + Finesse","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"L’utilisateur se précipite en avant, s'enveloppant de neige et devenant indétectable jusqu'à la fin du round. Cette technique facilite également les terrains difficiles, et réussit automatiquement les tests de dissimulation.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-02-blizzard-nocturne-infini","name":"Blizzard Nocturne Infini","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":2,"costE":6.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"2d8 + Finesse","damageText":"2d8 + Finesse\n\nUnique*\n\nEn forme de cône\n*Les effets de cette attaque se propagent en forme de cône ; le joueur choisit la direction.","range":4.5,"rangeText":"4.5m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"L'utilisateur bondit en avant, tournant et tranchant en plein air tout en avançant. Le sabreur déchaîne une violente démonstration de coups devant lui.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow","cone"],"specialLines":["Unique*","En forme de cône","*Les effets de cette attaque se propagent en forme de cône ; le joueur choisit la direction."],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"cone","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":true,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-03-grele-de-cendres-d-argent","name":"Grêle de Cendres d'Argent","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":3,"costE":8.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"3d6 + Force/Finesse","damageText":"3d6 + Force/Finesse\n\nFendre\n*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée","range":3.0,"rangeText":"3m","modifierText":"Finesse / Force","attackStat":"force-or-finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"L'utilisateur donne un coup de pied vers le haut dans une rotation aérienne ascendante, dispersant des coups d'épée dans toutes les directions comme une tourmente de flocons de neige.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow","aoe"],"specialLines":["Fendre","*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"allInRange","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":true,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-04-gelee-soudain-avalanche","name":"Gelée Soudain, Avalanche","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":4,"costE":13.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"2d20 + Force","damageText":"2d20 + Force\n\nTemps de charge\n* Nécessite un tour pour se charger\n** Une attaque interrompt la charge","range":9.0,"rangeText":"9m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"Au son des arbres gelés qui craquent, l'utilisateur avance et abaisse sa lame avec un poids soudain et écrasant. L'attaque imite une montée en puissance rappelant les frappes iai.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow","charge"],"specialLines":["Temps de charge","* Nécessite un tour pour se charger","** Une attaque interrompt la charge"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":1,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":1,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-05-femme-de-neige","name":"Femme de Neige","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":5,"costE":5.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d10 + Finesse","damageText":"1d10 + Finesse\n\nPousuivant\n*Impossible d'y réagir ou de l'éviter","range":3.0,"rangeText":"3m","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"Le sabreur prend une posture immobile comme possédé. Son prochain coup est trompeusement rapide, élégant et inévitable, comme un fantôme glissant à travers le givre.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow"],"specialLines":["Pousuivant","*Impossible d'y réagir ou de l'éviter"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":true,"cannotBeReactedTo":true,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-06-tranche-fendante-du-flocon","name":"Tranche Fendante du Flocon","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":6,"costE":1.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8 + Finesse","damageText":"1d8 + Finesse\n\nDéflecteur / Neutralisateur\n*Annule les dégâts subis","range":1.5,"rangeText":"1.5m / CàC","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"Une rafale rapide de mouvements d'épée qui vise les points faibles, divisant les projectiles, armes ou membres entrants comme des flocons de neige se séparant au contact.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow","deflect"],"specialLines":["Déflecteur / Neutralisateur","*Annule les dégâts subis"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":true,"negateIncomingDamage":true,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":true}}}
{"_id":"tech-snow-07-foret-de-juhyo-en-marche","name":"Forêt de Juhyo en Marche","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":7,"costE":9.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d20 + Force","damageText":"1d20 + Force","range":6.0,"rangeText":"6m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"Le sabreur se déplace à travers ses ennemis, frappant dans un rythme lent mais imparable. Son souffle laisse une traînée visible, ressemblant à une forêt enneigée d'arbres couverts de glace de la forêt Juhyo.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"techSnow000001","name":"Enterrement Silencieux","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-bubbles-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de la Neige","breathKey":"snow","breathLabel":"Souffle de la Neige","form":8,"costE":15.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"4d8 + Force","damageText":"4d8 + Force\n\nFendre\n*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée","range":3.0,"rangeText":"3m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de la Neige","description":"L'utilisateur canalise son souffle et glisse en avant en silence complet, la lame raclant le sol. Une explosion retardée de pression gelée propulse la lame dans une tranche multi-coupante.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","snow","aoe"],"specialLines":["Fendre","*Frappe tous les ennemis à portée"],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"allInRange","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":true,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-ocean-01-mer-des-epees","name":"Mer des Épées","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":1,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"L'épéiste vole vers l'avant, court sur les surfaces de l'eau, entrant en contact avec chacun de ses 7 coups d'épée sur son adversaire. Chaque contact avec l'eau propulse l'adversaire dans une nouvelle direction, permettant ainsi au sabreur de lancer une nouvelle attaque.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-ocean-02-saut-du-carpe-chagrin","name":"Saut du Carpe Chagrin","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":2,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"Un coup de lame montant crée un gigantesque tourbillon d'eau en dessous. Trois coups de lame successifs dessinent la forme d'une porte géante, suivis d'un coup de lame descendant.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-ocean-03-breche","name":"Brèche","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":3,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":4.5,"rangeText":"4.5m","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"Avec un coup de sabre montant effectué rapidement en mouvement horizontal, le combattant crée un tourbillon en forme de baleine géante, infligeant des dégâts à toutes les unités situées à moins de 4,5 mètres du point de saut et d'atterrissage.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-ocean-04-raie-emportee-par-le-vent-gracieux-vol","name":"Raie emportée par le vent, gracieux vol","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":4,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Finesse","attackStat":"finesse","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"L'épéiste glisse comme une raie manta, délivrant des coups de grande envergure en larges arcs. Chaque mouvement est imprévisible, ce qui lui permet d'esquiver les attaques tout en infligeant des coups précis.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-ocean-05-blocus-des-recifs-en-larmes","name":"Blocus des Récifs en Larmes","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":5,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"L'épéiste élève un mur d'eau en cascade pour bloquer les attaques entrantes. Cette barrière absorbe les dégâts et envoie des contre-vagues vers l'adversaire.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
