{"_id":"tech-ocean-07-fracas-de-l-umibozu","name":"Fracas de l’Umibozu","type":"technique","img":"icons/magic/water/water-wave-swirls-blue.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ocean","breathKey":"ocean","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ocean","form":7,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"Force","attackStat":"force","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ocean","description":"L'épéiste délivre une frappe descendante qui crée une onde de choc ressemblant à une vague déferlante. La force de ce coup assomme les ennemis et les repousse violemment.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","ocean"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
{"_id":"tech-west-01-diable-de-poussiere-mercuriel","name":"Diable de poussière mercuriel","type":"technique","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-barrel.webp","system":{"breath":"Souffle de l'Ouest","breathKey":"west","breathLabel":"Souffle de l'Ouest","form":1,"costE":0.0,"costRp":0,"costBdp":0,"damage":"1d8","damageText":"","range":1.5,"rangeText":"","modifierText":"","attackStat":"","autoHit":true,"isBreath":true,"sourceSection":"Souffle de l'Ouest","description":"L'épéiste dégaine sa lame à une vitesse explosive, délivrant un seul coup rapide comme l'éclair. La force de cette attaque crée un effet de vide, déséquilibrant ainsi les adversaires.","usageNote":"","tags":["breath","west"],"specialLines":[],"automation":{"requiresBreath":true,"area":"single","alternativeMode":"","lineOnly":false,"ranged":false,"unlimitedRange":false,"chargeTurns":0,"cooldownTurns":0,"cannotBeDodged":false,"cannotBeReactedTo":false,"deflect":false,"negateIncomingDamage":false,"afflictionStacks":0,"enduranceRestore":"none"},"flags":{"aoe":false,"antiFriendlyFire":false,"mobility":false,"decapitation":false,"charge":0,"deflect":false}}}
